      <title>北约盟国敦促谨慎对待针对乌克兰的1000亿美元援助计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/nato-allies-urge-caution-over-100-billion-aid-plan-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北约盟国正在控制对拟议的 1000 亿美元支持乌克兰基金的可行性的预期，因为该联盟正在努力解决如何向基辅提供足够的援助以长期抵御俄罗斯入侵的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/nato-allies-urge-caution-over-100-billion-aid-plan-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 12:18:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
