    <item>
      <title>法国敦促欧盟采取措施重新平衡对华贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/france-pushes-eu-for-measures-to-re-balance-trade-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国将游说欧盟采取措施，根据环境标准重新平衡与中国的贸易，因为法国看到大量中国产品涌入欧盟市场对经济构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/france-pushes-eu-for-measures-to-re-balance-trade-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 11:21:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯在哈尔科夫致命袭击后瞄准权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ukraine-says-four-killed-in-russian-drone-attack-on-kharkiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯军队一夜之间加大了对乌克兰第二大城市的攻击力度，这是最近针对该国电力基础设施的行动的一部分，此次攻击的强度超过了去年类似的攻击强度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ukraine-says-four-killed-in-russian-drone-attack-on-kharkiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 06:29:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
