    <item>
      <title>巴黎俱乐部将埃塞俄比亚与国际货币基金组织的交易期限延长至六月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/paris-club-said-to-extend-ethiopia-s-imf-deal-deadline-to-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据称，主要由发达国家债权人组成的巴黎俱乐部已将埃塞俄比亚与国际货币基金组织达成初步救助协议的最后期限延长三个月至六月底。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/paris-club-said-to-extend-ethiopia-s-imf-deal-deadline-to-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 17:54:28 GMT</pubDate>
